nd%20above%20all%2C%20unopposed%20aerial%20bombing%20of%20Gaza%20over%20the%20past%2080-odd%20days%20by%20the%20Israel%20Defense%20Forces%20(IDF)%20can%20be%20likened%20to%20hunting%20big%20game%20in%20a%20zoo%20or%20game%20reserve.%20It%20exceeds%20the%20ghastly%20redux%20of%20what%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20backers%20%E2%80%93%20the%20US%20and%20Britain%20%E2%80%93%20executed%20during%20the%20months%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20end%20of%20the%20second%20world%20war%2C%20by%20carpet%20bombing%20the%20German%20city%20of%20Dresden%20and%2C%20like%20Gaza%2C%20reducing%20it%20to%20rubble.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20four%20consecutive%20raids%20between%20February%2013-15%2C%201945%20by%20772%20Royal%20Air%20Force%20(RAF)%20%C2%A0heavy%20bombers%20and%20527%20of%20the%20United%20States%20Army%20Air%20Force%20(USAAF)%20dropped%20more%20than%203%2C900%20tons%20of%20ordnance%20and%20incendiary%20devices%20on%20Dresden%2C%20capital%20of%20the%20German%20state%20of%20Saxony%2C%20killing%20over%2025%2C000%20people.%20Like%20the%20RAF%20and%20the%20USAAF%2C%20the%20IDF%2C%20nearly%20eight%20decades%20later%20faced%20no%20airborne%20resistance%20in%20fulfilling%20its%20blood%20lust%20by%20raining%20death%20and%20destruction%20on%20an%20industrial%20scale%2C%20largely%20upon%20a%20civilian%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubsequent%20reports%20and%20analyses%20%E2%80%9Cjustified%E2%80%9D%20the%20Dresden%20bombings%2C%20much%20like%20the%20IDF%20is%20trying%20to%20do%20today%2C%20on%20grounds%20of%20strategic%20and%20political%20exigency.%20But%2C%20over%20intervening%20years%20%2Cjurists%20and%20human%20rights%20activists%20had%20maintained%20that%20indiscriminately%20pounding%20Dresden%20constituted%20a%20heinous%20war%20crime%2C%20as%20the%20ongoing%20bombing%20of%20Gaza%20was%20already%20being%20defined%20almost%20daily%20in%20world%20capitals%2C%20including%20London%20and%20Washington%2C%20by%20millions%20of%20protesting%20citizens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20October%207%2C%20the%20IDF%2C%20according%20to%20the%20US%E2%80%99s%20Office%20of%20the%20Director%20of%20National%20Intelligence%20assessments%2C%20had%20conducted%20strategic%20bombing%20missions%20over%20Gaza%2C%20dropping%20over%2029%2C000%20tonnes%20of%20air-to-ground%20munitions%20across%20a%20365%20sq.%20km%20area%2C%20or%20nearly%2080%20lbs%20of%20killer%20ordnance%20per%20sq.%20km.%20This%20was%20aimed%20egregiously%20into%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20most%20densely%20populated%20region%20that%20includes%20eight%20refugee%20camps%20and%20a%20population%20density%20of%206%2C507%20persons%20per%20sq.%20km.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsequently%2C%20these%20unremitting%20IDF%20air%20strikes%20have%20significantly%20added%20to%20the%20overall%20Palestinian%20death%20toll%2C%20which%20currently%20totals%20around%2021%2C000%20people%2C%20including%20some%206%2C000%20children.%20Another%2055%2C000-odd%20Palestinians%20had%20been%20wounded%2C%20with%20little%20or%20no%20recourse%20to%20medical%20assistance%2C%20or%20hope%20of%20any%20kind%20in%20a%20war-ravaged%20and%20besieged%20Gaza%2C%20according%20to%20multiple%20human%20rights%20organisations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fhow-the-war-in-gaza-is-reshaping-geopolitics%5C%22%3EHow%20the%20War%20in%20Gaza%20Is%20Reshaping%20Geopolitics%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20December%2014%20report%2C%20CNN%2C%20quoting%20unnamed%20US%20intelligence%20sources%2C%20claimed%20that%2045%25%20of%20this%20killer%20ordnance%20delivered%20aerially%2C%20comprised%20unguided%20bunker%20busters%2C%20or%20free-fall%20%E2%80%98dumb%20bombs%E2%80%99%20that%20were%20not%20fitted%20with%20any%20guidance%20systems.%20In%20its%20website%20report%20it%20declared%20that%20if%20the%20IDF%20was%20employing%20unguided%20munitions%20at%20the%20rate%2C%20like%20the%20US%20Office%20of%20the%20Director%20of%20National%20Intelligence%20believes%20it%20was%2C%20then%20it%20simply%20%E2%80%98undercut%E2%80%99%20Tel%20Aviv%E2%80%99s%20claims%20of%20%C2%A0trying%20to%20minimise%20civilian%20casualties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECNN%20further%20went%20on%20to%20state%20that%20the%20US%20had%20supplied%20Israel%20some%203%2C000%20of%20these%20joint%20direct%20attack%20munitions%20(JDAMs)%20since%20October%207%20after%20the%20Gaza%20offensive%20began%2C%20following%20Hamas%E2%80%99s%20cross-border%20raid%20on%20multiple%20Israeli%20targets%2C%20in%20which%20some%201%2C200%20people%2C%20including%20women%20and%20children%2C%20were%20killed%20and%20hundreds%20of%20others%20kidnapped.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20experts%2C%20the%20blast%20from%20these%201%2C000-2%2C000-odd%20pound%20JDAMs%20in%20open%20spaces%20meant%20%E2%80%98instant%20death%E2%80%99%20for%20anyone%20within%20a%2030-metre%20radius%3B%20lethal%20fragmentation%20from%20them%20extended%20around%20365m.%20In%20an%20October%2031%20strike%20on%20the%20urban%20refugee%20camp%20of%20Jabaliya%20at%20the%20northern%20end%20of%20the%20Gaza%20strip%2C%20a%202%2C000-pound%20unguided%20JDAM%20had%20instantly%20killed%20over%20100%20civilians%2C%20according%20to%20news%20reports%20from%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDetailed%20accounts%20from%20the%20battle%20zone%20also%20revealed%20that%20the%20IDF%20frequently%20dive-bombed%20its%20ground%20targets%20with%20JDAMs%2C%20rendering%20their%20impact%20even%20more%20lethal.%C2%A0%20Marc%20Garlasco%2C%20a%20former%20Pentagon%20official%20and%20United%20Nations%20war%20crimes%20investigator%20told%20the%20Associated%20Press%20(AP)%20recently%20that%20these%20JDAMS%20turn%20%E2%80%98earth%20to%20liquid%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98pancaked%20entire%20buildings%E2%80%99.%20Other%20Western%20military%20analysts%20concurred%20that%20the%20rate%20at%20which%20Israel%20was%20using%20these%20dumb%20bombs%20was%20%E2%80%98contributing%20significantly%E2%80%99%20to%20the%20soaring%20Palestinian%20death%20toll.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20unclear%2C%20however%2C%20in%20the%20fog%20of%20war%2C%20the%20high%20level%20of%20secrecy%20prevailing%20over%20the%20conflict%20and%20lack%20of%20access%20provided%20by%20Israel%20to%20independent%20news%20reporters%2C%20the%20exact%20nature%20of%20these%20killer%20bombs.%20But%20experts%20claimed%20some%20of%20them%20to%20be%20US-origin%20M117%E2%80%99s%20that%20were%20used%20extensively%20by%20the%20US%20Air%20Force%20in%20the%20Vietnam%20War%2C%20and%20thereafter%20during%20Operation%20Desert%20Storm%20against%20the%20Iraqi%20military%2C%20in%20the%20early%201990%E2%80%99s%2C%20with%20devastating%20effect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECNN%20and%20other%20US%20media%20also%20reported%20that%20the%20US%20had%20provided%20Israel%20with%20assorted%20unguided%20bombs%2C%20including%205%2C000%20Mk82s%20and%20its%20variants.%20These%20were%20500-pound%20low-drag%2C%20general%20purpose%20aircraft%20bombs%20containing%20around%20200%20lbs%20of%20high%20explosive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20bad%20enough%20to%20be%20using%20these%20weapons%20(bombs)%20when%20they%20are%20precisely%20hitting%20their%20targets%2C%E2%80%9D%20Brian%20Castner%2C%20a%20weapons%20investigator%20and%20ordnance%20expert%20with%20Amnesty%20International%20told%20CNN.%20However%2C%20it%20is%20a%20massive%20civilian%20harm%20problem%20if%20they%20do%20not%20have%20that%20accuracy%2C%20and%20if%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20even%20determine%20whether%20the%20bomb%20is%20actually%20landing%20where%20the%20IDF%20intended%20it%20to%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fpalestine-palestinians-and-the-western-liberals-burden%5C%22%3EPalestine%2C%20Palestinians%20and%20the%20Western%20Liberal%E2%80%99s%20Burden%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20widespread%20criticism%2C%20including%20from%20United%20Nations%20bodies%2C%20the%20US%20has%20quietly%20continued%20to%20supply%20materiel%2C%20including%20JDAMs%20to%20Israel%2C%20notwithstanding%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%E2%80%99s%20somewhat%20disingenuous%20claim%20that%20Tel%20Aviv%20was%20%E2%80%98losing%20international%20legitimacy%E2%80%99%20for%20what%20he%20termed%20its%20%E2%80%98indiscriminate%20bombings%E2%80%99.%20Other%20senior%20US%20officials%20also%20duplicitously%20iterated%20IDF%E2%80%99s%20preposterous%20assertions%20that%20it%20was%20%E2%80%98doing%20everything%E2%80%99%20to%20reduce%20civilian%20casualties%20in%20its%20ongoing%20Gaza%20offensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20CNN%20revealed%20that%20the%20remaining%2055%25%20or%20so%20of%20ordnance%20used%20by%20the%20IDF%20in%20its%20unchallenged%20bombing%20were%20the%20even%20more%20destructive%20precision%20guided%20munitions%20(PGMs)%20that%20included%202%2C000-pound%20bombs%20guided%20by%20%E2%80%98Smart%2C%20Precise%2C%20Cost-Effective%E2%80%99%20or%20SPICE%20kits%2C%20equipped%20with%20GPS%20guidance%20systems%20for%20greater%20accuracy.%20It%20reported%20recently%20that%20the%20US%20planned%20on%20transferring%20%24320%20million%20worth%20of%20SPICE%20kits%20to%20Israel%2C%20manufactured%20by%20the%20US%20subsidiary%20of%20Raphael%20Advanced%20Defence%20Systems%20in%20Haifa%20that%20originally%20developed%20these%20precision%20enablers%20for%20assorted%20air-to-ground%20missiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20may%20be%20recalled%20that%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%E2%80%99s%20Mirage%202000Hs%20which%20conducted%20the%20punitive%20raid%20on%20an%20alleged%20Islamist%20terrorist%20camp%20in%20Balakot%20in%20north-west%20Pakistan%20in%20February%202019%20%E2%80%93%20in%20response%20to%20the%20fatal%20bombing%20of%20a%20bus%20carrying%20Indian%20paramilitaries%20in%20Kashmir%20%E2%80%93%20also%20employed%20Israel-supplied%20SPICE%20kits%20to%20deliver%20Paveway%20II%20laser-guided%20bombs%20to%20their%20intended%20targets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20in%20a%20disagreeable%20flashback%20to%20the%20second%20world%20war%20Dresden%20raids%2C%20Israel%2C%20like%20the%20RAF%20and%20the%20RAAF%2C%20also%20resorted%20to%20air%20dropping%20Arabic%20leaflets%20into%20Gazan%20towns%2C%20warning%20Palestinian%20civilians%20to%20vacate%20their%20homes%20ahead%20of%20impending%20bombing%20raids.%20And%20much%20like%20the%20former%2C%20the%20IDF%20leaflets%20too%20announced%20their%20unambiguous%20intent%20to%20carry%20out%20aerial%20strikes%2C%20warning%20all%20Gaza%20residents%20against%20disregarding%20these%20warnings%20at%20their%20peril.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Dresden%20leaflets%20as%20paraphrased%20by%20American%20satirist%20Kurt%20Vonnegut%20Jr.%20%E2%80%93%20who%2C%20as%20a%20US%20army%20prisoner%20of%20war%20was%20interned%20in%20the%20city%20during%20its%20bombing%20and%20survived%20in%20a%20meat%20locker%20in%20a%20local%20slaughterhouse%20%E2%80%93%20starkly%20stated%20that%20%E2%80%9Cdestruction%20of%20anything%20other%20than%20military%20objectives%20was%20unintentional%20and%20the%20unavoidable%20fortunes%20of%20war%E2%80%9D.%20After%20the%20war%2C%20Vonnegut%20wrote%20%3Cem%3ESlaughterhouse-Five%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20semi-autobiographical%20anti-war%20novel%20of%20Dresden%E2%80%99s%20fire-bombing%20by%20the%20Allies%20that%20went%20on%20to%20become%20a%20best-seller%20in%20the%201970s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20little%20seems%20to%20have%20changed%20since%201945%20in%20the%20five%20basic%20principles%20governing%20the%20legal%20use%20of%20force%20by%20the%20powerful%20in%20an%20armed%20conflict.%20These%20incorporate%20military%20necessity%2C%20distinction-whereby%20attackers%20need%20to%20distinguish%20between%20combatants%20and%20civilians-proportionality%2C%20humanity%20and%20honour%20or%20chivalry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENone%20it%20appears%20existed%20then%2C%20and%20certainly%20none%20do%20now%2C%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703764820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F27180005%2F2048px-2017.03.26_