obic%20got%20her%20start%20at%20Chubb%2025%20years%20ago%2C%20as%20an%20intern%20in%20Canada.%20Now%20she's%20the%20division%20president%20of%20the%20insurance%20company's%20personal%20risk%20services%20in%20North%20America.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%20a%20way%20to%20get%20through%20the%20summer%20doing%20%26quot%3Bthe%20lame%20insurance%20thing%26quot%3B%20turned%20into%20a%20career%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChubb%20is%20a%20commercial%20and%20personal%20property-%20and%20casualty-insurance%20company%20that%20focuses%20on%20insuring%20the%20homes%2C%20cars%2C%20toys%2C%20jewelry%2C%20and%20wine%20of%20high-net-worth%20individuals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople's%20expectations%20of%20this%20industry%20are%20generally%20quite%20wrong%2C%26quot%3B%20Robic%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20She's%20worked%20on%20the%20commercial%20and%20personal%20sides%20of%20the%20business%2C%20including%20in%20underwriting.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20deemed%20as%20sexy%2C%20but%20that%20was%20by%20far%20one%20of%20the%20most%20rewarding%20jobs%20I%20had%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20she%20acknowledged%20that%20luck%20had%20been%20a%20factor%20in%20her%20career%2C%20she%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bself-advocacy%20is%20nothing%20to%20be%20ashamed%20of.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20growing%20focus%20for%20Chubb%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chubb.com%2Fhk-en%2Farticles%2Fbuilding-your-wealth-legacy.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewealth%20transfer%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20helping%20wealthy%20people%20pass%20on%20things%20like%20collector%20cars%2C%20a%20second%20home%2C%20a%20watch%20collection%2C%20or%20a%20wine%20collection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20makes%20insurance%20unique%2C%20Robic%20said%2C%20is%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20thing%20you're%20promising%20people%20doesn't%20change.%26quot%3B%20She%20described%20insurance%20as%20a%20promise.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20saying%20trust%20me%20%E2%80%94%20should%20something%20go%20wrong%2C%20you've%20given%20me%20all%20this%20money%20for%20that%20promise%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20a%20bad%20day%20comes%20when%20our%20clients%20are%20at%20their%20worst%2C%20we%20should%20be%20at%20our%20best.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERobic's%20insights%20are%20part%20of%20Business%20Insider's%20year-end%20leadership%20package%2C%20%26quot%3BLooking%20Ahead%202024%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20digs%20into%20vision%2C%20strategy%2C%20and%20challenges%20across%20corporate%20America.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20following%20interview%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat's%20one%20thing%20you're%20excited%20about%20for%202024%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20super%20excited%20that%20my%20almost-17-year-old%20daughter%20will%20get%20her%20driver's%20license%20in%20January%2C%20going%20on%20to%20drive%20all%20over%20New%20Jersey%20for%20volleyball%20tournaments.%20But%20I'm%20also%20most%20concerned%20about%20that%2C%20because%20it's%20scary%20when%20your%20kid%20starts%20driving%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20if%20you're%20a%20mother%20in%20the%20insurance%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20business%20side%2C%20we're%20looking%20forward%20to%20continuing%20many%20of%20our%20employee%20engagement%20efforts%2C%20including%20getting%20some%20stronger%20outcomes%20from%20our%20DEI%20initiatives.%20It's%20an%20area%20we%20know%20we%20can%20be%20better%20in%2C%20and%20we've%20launched%20a%20bunch%20of%20internal%20efforts%20around%20improving%20diversity%20in%20all%20parts%20of%20our%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20firmly%20believe%20that%20greater%20diversity%20can%20better%20business%20outcomes.%20I'm%20looking%20forward%20to%20next%20year%20actually%20seeing%20some%20of%20the%20fruits%20of%20a%20lot%20of%20those%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20looking%20forward%20to%20attracting%20and%20retaining%20the%20best%20talent%20and%20having%20the%20composition%20of%20our%20employee%20teams%20continue%20to%20change%20so%20that%20they%20reflect%20the%20markets%20in%20which%20we%20operate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat's%20one%20thing%20you're%20concerned%20about%20for%202024%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20risk%20when%20you've%20got%20the%20lead%20in%20a%20race%20of%20getting%20complacent.%20And%20our%20clients%20have%20put%20us%20in%20the%20lead.%20We're%20very%20grateful%20for%20that%2C%20that%20they%20have%20that%20trust%20in%20us.%20We%20can%20afford%20to%20sit%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20the%20risk%20for%20us%20is%20continuing%20to%20build%20that%20culture%20and%20making%20sure%20that%20the%20team%20maintains%20that%20high%20bar%20%E2%80%94%20keeps%20up%20the%20energy%20and%20drive%20to%20achieve%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20one%20thing%20you%20got%20right%20in%202023%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20treating%20your%20clients%20like%20they're%20the%20center%20of%20all%20your%20success.%20Building%20a%20culture%20centered%20around%20creating%20the%20best%20client%20experience%20is%20something%20we%20spend%20a%20ton%20of%20time%20on.%20And%20it%20sounds%20silly%2C%20because%20it's%20insurance%2C%20and%20I%20think%20you're%20inundated%20with%20images%20on%20TV%20as%20to%20what%20insurance%20is.%20But%20it's%20really%20hard%20to%20get%20that%20right.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20clients%20choose%20Chubb%2C%20they%20expect%20that%20when%20something%20goes%20wrong%2C%20we're%20going%20to%20exceed%20their%20expectations%2C%20not%20just%20meet%20them.%20So%20figuring%20out%20how%20we%20do%20that%20day%20in%20and%20day%20out%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20your%20claim%20is%20something%20we%20work%20very%20hard%20at.%20I%20think%20we%20really%20got%20that%20right%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20things%20we%20measure%20is%20how%20often%20after%20a%20claim%20our%20clients%20tell%20us%20they're%20highly%20satisfied.%20And%20our%20score%20this%20year%20was%2094%25%20%E2%80%94%2094%25%20of%20the%20time%20our%20clients%20are%20highly%20satisfied.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20also%20have%20anecdotal%20evidence%2C%20which%20is%20not%20super%20scientific.%20Like%2C%20last%20week%20I%20was%20flying%20back%20from%20Dallas%2C%20and%20the%20guy%20beside%20me%20saw%20the%20job%20name%20on%20my%20laptop%20when%20I%20opened%20it.%20And%20he%20launched%20into%20this%20story%20about%20a%20tree%20getting%20hit%20by%20lightning%20six%20years%20ago%20at%20his%20house%20and%20how%20amazing%20we%20were.%20He%20will%20be%20a%20customer%20for%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20look%20at%20large%20catastrophes%2C%20like%20the%20Hawaiian%20wildfires.%20We%20were%20one%20of%20the%20first%20insurance%20companies%20on-site%20starting%20to%20rebuild%20people's%20lives.%20There's%20a%20point%20of%20pride%20in%20that%20knowing%20you're%20right%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat's%20one%20thing%20you%20got%20wrong%20in%202023%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20thing%20that%20we%20maybe%20got%20wrong%20was%20we%20weren't%20moving%20fast%20enough%20in%20some%20areas%20that%20are%20still%20full%20of%20opportunity%20for%20our%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20really%20growing%20this%20digital%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chubb.com%2Fus-en%2Fbusinesses%2Fresources%2Fwhat-is-embedded-insurance.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eembedded%20insurance%3C%2Fa%3E%20internationally%2C%20but%20in%20North%20America%20it's%20still%20sort%20of%20in%20its%20infancy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20if%20you%20go%20and%20buy%20a%20luxury%20good%20online%20%E2%80%94%20think%20a%20watch%20or%20jewelry%2C%20even%20potentially%20wine%20%E2%80%94%20I%20want%20to%20be%20able%20to%20sell%20you%20an%20insurance%20product%20that%20you%20might%20need%20right%20at%20that%20point%20of%20sale.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20started%20doing%20that%20with%20some%20partners.%20I%20just%20think%20there's%20a%20lot%20more%20opportunity.%20So%20we're%20ramping%20up%20our%20sales%20and%20technology%20teams%20to%20do%20that%20better%20and%20do%20more%20of%20that%20next%20year.%20It's%20just%20not%20moving%20fast%20enough%20is%20probably%20the%20regret.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20flood%20insurance%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0most%20people%20don't%20realize%20that's%20a%20separate%20purchase%20from%20your%20homeowners%20insurance.%20And%20less%20than%205%25%20of%20our%20customers%20buy%20flood%20insurance.%20We%20have%20a%20product%2C%20and%20we%20need%20to%20do%20a%20better%20job%20of%20explaining%20to%20others%20that%20for%20a%20very%20nominal%20cost%20you%20can%20protect%20yourself%20from%20something%20that%20is%20far%20more%20pervasive%20than%20you%20realize.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20just%20want%20to%20go%20faster%20in%20some%20of%20these%20places%20to%20deliver%20these%20products%20to%20our%20clients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchubb-insurance-outlook-wealth-transfer-flood-insurance-embedded-insurance-dei-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703763362000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657ca30e50edbc52a864e25d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchubb-insurance-outlook-wealth-transfer-flood-insurance-embedded-insurance-dei-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chubb's%20Ana%20Robic%20wants%20to%20move%20faster%20in%202024%20in%20areas%20including%20internal%20DEI%20efforts%20and%20awareness%20about%20flood%20insurance.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jrose%40insider.com%20(Jos%C3%A9e%20Rose)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchubb-insurance-outlook-wealth-transfer-flood-insurance-embedded-insurance-dei-2023-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pegasus%20Used%20to%20Target%20The%20Wire's%20Founding%20Editor%2C%20Reporter%20Working%20on%20Adani%2C%20Amnesty%20Confirms%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F08%2F02143130%2Fpegasus397131.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Amnesty%20International%E2%80%99s%20Security%20Lab%20says%20it%20has%20detected%20evidence%20that%20Pegasus%20spyware%20was%20used%20by%20an%20unknown%20government%20agency%20to%20compromise%20the%20mobile%20phones%20of%20two%20journalists%20in%20India%2C%20Siddharth%20Varadarajan%20of%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20Anand%20Mangnale%20of%20the%20Oraganised%20Crime%20and%20Corruption%20Reporting%20Project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmnesty%20released%20its%20findings%20on%20December%2028%20as%20part%20of%20its%20partnership%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farchive.is%2F2023.12.28-021126%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fworld%2F2023%2F12%2F27%2Findia-apple-iphone-hacking%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20wider%20investigation%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3EWashington%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20second%20time%20Varadarajan%20has%20been%20targeted%20with%20the%20Israeli%20made%20spyware.%20As%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20in%202021%20as%20part%20of%20an%20investigation%20by%20a%20worldwide%20media%20consortium%20known%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98Pegasus%20Project%E2%80%99%2C%20his%20phone%20was%20among%20several%20other%20journalists%2C%20opposition%20politicians%20and%20human%20rights%20defenders%20on%20whose%20devices%20Amnesty%E2%80%99s%20Security%20Lab%20found%20Pegasus.%20The%20presence%20of%20the%20spyware%20on%20Magnale%E2%80%99s%20phone%20is%20especially%20concerning%20as%20the%20trigger%20for%20his%20selection%20as%20a%20target%20appears%20to%20be%20his%20investigation%20into%20the%20business%20affairs%20of%20the%20Adani%20group.%20As%20the%20%3Cem%3EWashington%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%20reports%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9COn%20Aug.%2023%2C%20the%20OCCRP%20emailed%20Adani%20seeking%20comment%20for%20a%20story%20it%20would%20publish%20a%20week%20later%20alleging%20that%20his%20brother%20was%20part%3Cb%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3Eof%20a%20group%20that%20had%20secretly%20traded%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars%20worth%20of%20the%20Adani%20Group%20conglomerate%E2%80%99s%20public%20stock%2C%20possibly%20in%20violation%20of%20Indian%20securities%20law.%20A%20forensic%20analysis%20of%20Mangnale%E2%80%99s%20phone%2C%20conducted%20by%20Amnesty%20International%20and%20shared%20with%3Cb%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3EThe%20Washington%20Post%2C%20found%20that%20within%2024%20hours%20of%20that%20inquiry%2C%20an%20attacker%20infiltrated%20the%20device%20and%20planted%C2%A0Pegasus%2C%20the%20notorious%20spyware%C2%A0that%20was%20developed%20by%20Israeli%20company%20NSO%20Group%3Cb%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3Eand%20that%20NSO%20says%20is%20sold%20only%20to%20governments.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20latest%20findings%20show%20that%20increasingly%2C%20journalists%20in%20India%20face%20the%20threat%20of%20unlawful%20surveillance%20simply%20for%20doing%20their%20jobs%2C%20alongside%20other%20tools%20of%20repression%20including%20imprisonment%20under%20draconian%20laws%2C%20smear%20campaigns%2C%20harassment%2C%20and%20intimidation%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Donncha%20%C3%93%20Cearbhaill%2C%20head%20of%20Amnesty%20International%E2%80%99s%20Security%20Lab.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmnesty%20said%20its%20Security%20Lab%20%E2%80%9Cfirst%20observed%20indications%20of%20renewed%20Pegasus%20spyware%20threats%20towards%20individuals%20in%20India%20during%20a%20regular%20technical%20monitoring%20exercise%20in%20June%202023%2C%20a%20number%20of%20months%20after%20media%20reported%20that%20the%20Indian%20government%20was%20seeking%20to%20procure%20a%20new%20commercial%20spyware%20system.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Apple%20issued%20threat%20notifications%20globally%20to%20iPhone%20users%20who%20may%20have%20been%20targeted%20by%20%E2%80%9Cstate-sponsored%20attackers%E2%80%9D%2C%20Varadarajan%2C%20Mangnale%20and%20a%20number%20of%20other%20journalists%20and%20opposition%20politicians%20in%20India%20received%20the%20notifications.%20Among%20those%20who%20went%20public%20at%20the%20time%20were%20Mahua%20Moitra%20of%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%2C%20a%20prominent%20critic%20of%20the%20Adani%20group%2C%20and%20Ravi%20Nair%2C%20a%20journalist%20with%20OCCRP%20who%20was%20working%20on%20an%20Adani%20story%20with%20Mangnale.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Amnesty%20International%E2%80%99s%20Security%20Lab%20undertook%20a%20forensic%20analysis%20on%20the%20phones%20of%20Varadarajan%20and%20Mangnale%2C%20the%20press%20release%20said%2C%20it%20%E2%80%9Cfound%20traces%20of%20Pegasus%20spyware%20activity%20on%20devices%20owned%20by%20both%20Indian%20journalists%E2%80%9D%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Security%20Lab%20recovered%20evidence%20from%20Anand%20Mangnale%E2%80%99s%20device%20of%20a%20zero-click%20exploit%20which%20was%20sent%20to%20his%20phone%20over%20iMessage%20on%2023%20August%202023%2C%20and%20designed%20to%20covertly%20install%20the%20Pegasus%20spyware.%20The%20phone%20was%20running%20iOS%2016.6%2C%20the%20latest%20version%20available%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CA%20zero-click%20exploit%20refers%20to%20malicious%20software%20that%20enables%20spyware%20to%20be%20installed%20on%20a%20device%20without%20requiring%20any%20user%20action%20from%20the%20target%2C%20such%20as%20clicking%20on%20a%20link.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Security%20Lab%20also%20identified%20an%20attacker-controlled%20email%20address%20used%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Pegasus%20attack%20on%20his%20device.%20The%20recovered%20samples%20are%20consistent%20with%20the%20NSO%20Group%E2%80%99s%20BLASTPASS%20exploit%2C%20publicly%20identified%20by%20Citizen%20Lab%20in%20September%202023%20and%20patched%20by%20Apple%20in%20iOS%2016.6.1%20(CVE-2023-41064).%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CAnand%20Mangnale%E2%80%99s%20phone%20was%20vulnerable%20to%20this%20zero-click%20exploit%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20attack.%20It%20is%20currently%20unclear%20if%20the%20exploit%20attempt%20resulted%20in%20a%20successful%20compromise%20of%20his%20device.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20Varadarajan%E2%80%99s%20phone%2C%20Amnesty%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsecuritylab.amnesty.org%2Flatest%2F2023%2F12%2Fpegasus-zero-click-exploit-threatens-journalists-in-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eforensic%20report%20notes%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Security%20Lab%20reviewed%20forensic%20records%20from%20Siddharth%20Varadarajan%E2%80%99s%20iPhone%2011%20and%20identified%20traces%20which%20confirms%20that%20his%20phone%20was%20also%20target%20with%20NSO%20Group%E2%80%99s%20Pegasus%20spyware%20in%20October%202023.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CHomeKit%20logs%20from%20Siddharth%20Varadarajan%20iPhone%20show%20that%20the%20was%20also%20targeted%20by%20the%20same%20Pegasus%20attacker%20email%20account%20used%20to%20target%20Anand%20Mangnale.%20The%20recovered%20HomeKit%20logs%20show%20that%20the%20%3Cstrong%3Enatalymarinova%40proton.me%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Apple%20account%20interacted%20with%20his%20device%E2%80%99s%20HomeKit%20service%20on%2016%20October%202023%20around%2014%3A36%3A09%20UTC.%20At%20the%20time%20his%20phone%20was%20running%20iOS%20version%2016.6.1%20which%20was%20not%20vulnerable%20to%20the%20BLASTPAST%20attack.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Cem%3EWashington%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20that%20iVerify%2C%20a%20New%20York%20security%20firm%20it%20engaged%20to%20test%20the%20phones%20of%20some%20of%20the%20Indian%20politicians%20on%20the%20list%20of%20those%20who%20received%20a%20spyware%20alert%20from%20Apple%2C%20found%20tell-tale%20footprints%20of%20targetting%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CIVerify%20examined%20Moitra%E2%80%99s%20phone%20backup%20and%20confirmed%20that%20she%20had%20received%20an%20Apple%20warning.%3Cb%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3EIt%20also%20saw%20urgent%20crash%20reports%20that%2C%20together%20with%20other%20digital%20records%2C%20suggested%20the%20device%20had%20been%20hacked.%20The%20company%20also%20found%20a%20threat%20notification%20and%20suspicious%20activity%20on%20the%20phone%20of%20Praveen%20Chakravarty%2C%20head%20of%20the%20opposition%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20party%E2%80%99s%20data%20analytics%20department.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20renewed%20evidence%20of%20Pegasus%20being%20used%20against%20journalists%20in%20India%20comes%20more%20than%20a%20year%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20noted%20that%20the%20technical%20committee%20it%20had%20appointed%20to%20probe%20allegations%20of%20illegal%20surveillance%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-pegasus-technical-committee%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efound%20evidence%20of%20%E2%80%9Cmalware%E2%80%99%20in%20as%20many%20as%20five%20mobile%20phones%20which%20it%20tested%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20then%20chief%20justice%20of%20India%2C%20N.V.%20Ramana%2C%20had%20also%20said%20that%20that%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20had%20refused%20to%20cooperate%20with%20the%20committee%20%E2%80%93%20despite%20being%20asked%20by%20the%20court%20to%20do%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20technical%20committee%20was%20created%20in%20the%20face%20of%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20refusal%20to%20confirm%20or%20deny%20its%20purchase%20and%20use%20of%20Pegasus%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20not%20held%20the%20government%20in%20contempt%20and%20has%20also%20not%20taken%20any%20further%20action%20on%20the%20findings%20it%20has.%20The%20committee%E2%80%99s%20report%20itself%20was%20not%20made%20public%2C%20citing%20privacy%20concerns%2C%20though%20some%20of%20the%20journalists%20who%20had%20submitted%20their%20devices%20for%20testing%20had%20said%20they%20had%20no%20objection%20to%20the%20committee%E2%80%99s%20report%20being%20released.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPressure%20on%20Apple%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%3Cem%3E%20Washington%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%20story%20also%20documents%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20attempts%20to%20control%20the%20narrative%20soon%20after%20Apple%E2%80%99s%20October%20notiications%20were%20issued%2C%20which%20included%20putting%20pressure%20on%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20executives%20in%20India%20to%20themselves%20downplay%20the%20significance%20of%20the%20warning%20they%20had%20just%20issued%20to%20iPhone%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20data-qa%3D%5C%22article-body%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20dir%3D%5C%22null%5C%22%20data-testid%3D%5C%22drop-cap-letter%5C%22%20data-el%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CSenior%20Modi%20administration%20officials%20called%20Apple%20India%E2%80%99s%20managing%20director%2C%20Virat%20Bhatia%2C%20after%20the%20news%20broke%2C%20said%20two%20people%20with%20knowledge%20of%20the%20matter.%20One%20of%20the%20people%20said%20Indian%20officials%20asked%20Apple%20to%20withdraw%20the%20warnings%20and%20say%20it%20had%20made%20a%20mistake.%20After%20a%20heated%20discussion%2C%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20India%20office%20said%20the%20most%20it%20could%20do%20was%20put%20out%20a%20public%20statement%20that%20emphasized%20certain%20caveats%20that%20Apple%20had%20already%20listed%20on%20its%20tech%20support%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farchive.is%2Fo%2FtjMEN%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fsupport.apple.com%2Fen-in%2F102174%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epage%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3Eabout%20the%20warnings.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703763294000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fpegasus-used-to-target-the-wires-founding-editor-reporter-working-on-adani-amnesty-confirms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20OCCRP%20sent%20queries%20to%20the%20Adani%20group%20on%20August%2024%20and%20%26quot%3Bwithin%2024%20hours%20of%20that%20inquiry%2C%20an%20attacker%20infiltrated%20the%20device%20and%20planted%C2%A0Pegasus%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20phone%20of%20its%20reporter%2C%20Anand%20Mangnale%2C%20the%20Washington%20Post%20and%20Amnesty%20International%20have%20reported.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Qatar%20Court%20Commutes%20Indian%20Navy%20Veterans'%20Death%20Sentence%20to%20Prison%20Terms%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F24160310%2FCourt-of-appeals.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Two%20months%20after%20sentencing%20eight%20Indian%20Navy%20veterans%20to%20death%2C%20Qatar%E2%80%99s%20Court%20of%20Appeal%20reduced%20their%20capital%20punishment%20to%20imprisonment%20of%20varying%20terms%20on%20Thursday%20(December%2028).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20(MEA)%20noted%20the%20%E2%80%9Cverdict%20today%20of%20the%20Court%20of%20Appeal%20of%20Qatar%20in%20the%20Dahra%20Global%20case%2C%20in%20which%20the%20sentences%20have%20been%20reduced%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ministry%20said%20that%20Vipul%2C%20the%20Indian%20ambassador%20to%20Qatar%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20veterans%E2%80%99%20family%20members%20were%20present%20in%20the%20Court%20of%20Appeal%20when%20the%20order%20was%20delivered.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStating%20that%20a%20detailed%20judgement%20is%20awaited%2C%20the%20MEA%20said%20that%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Cin%20close%20touch%20with%20the%20legal%20team%20as%20well%20as%20the%20family%20members%20to%20decide%20on%20the%20next%20steps%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20usual%2C%20the%20ministry%20explained%20that%20it%20would%20not%20make%20any%20further%20comments%20at%20this%20juncture%20%E2%80%9Cdue%20to%20the%20confidential%20and%20sensitive%20nature%20of%20proceedings%20of%20this%20case%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20stood%20by%20them%20since%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20matter%20and%20we%20will%20continue%20to%20extend%20all%20consular%20and%20legal%20assistance.%20We%20will%20also%20continue%20to%20take%20up%20the%20matter%20with%20the%20Qatari%20authorities%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20was%20no%20mention%20of%20the%20extent%20to%20which%20the%20veterans%E2%80%99%20sentences%20were%20reduced%2C%20but%20it%20is%20understood%20that%20they%20have%20been%20given%20varying%20prison%20terms.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20eight%20men%20are%20Captain%20Navtej%20Singh%20Gill%2C%20Captain%20Birendra%20Kumar%20Verma%2C%20Captain%20Saurabh%20Vasisht%2C%20Commodore%20Amit%20Nagpal%2C%20Commodore%20Purnendu%20Tiwari%2C%20Commodore%20Sugunakar%20Pakala%2C%20Commodore%20Sanjeev%20Gupta%20and%20Sailor%20Ragesh.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fqatar-eight-former-indian-navy-officers-handed-death-penalty%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20October%2026%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Qatar%E2%80%99s%20Court%20of%20First%20Instance%20handed%20the%20death%20penalty%20to%20the%20veterans%2C%20who%20had%20been%20detained%20for%20over%20a%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEmployed%20by%20the%20now-defunct%20Omani%20private%20firm%20Dahra%20Global%20Technologies%20and%20Consultancy%20Services%2C%20they%20were%20contracted%20for%20providing%20training%20and%20related%20services%20to%20Qatar%E2%80%99s%20armed%20forces.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20charges%20have%20never%20been%20made%20public%2C%20media%20reports%20hinted%20at%20the%20possibility%20of%20their%20being%20charged%20with%20espionage.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20had%20said%20that%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Cdeeply%20shocked%E2%80%9D%20by%20the%20October%20verdict%2C%20but%20had%20even%20then%20refrained%20from%20making%20further%20comments.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAbout%20four%20weeks%20later%2C%20the%20Court%20of%20Appeal%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fqatar-court-accepts-appeal-application-against-death-sentence-to-8-indian-navy-veterans%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eaccepted%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20deliberations%20the%20Indian%20government%E2%80%99s%20appeal%20against%20the%20veterans%E2%80%99%20death%20sentence.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703763283000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F24160310%2FCourt-of-appeals.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fqatar-court-commutes-death-sentence-given-to-eight-indian-navy-veterans%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20external%20affairs%20ministry%20said%20it%20would%20not%20make%20any%20further%20comments%20at%20this%20juncture%20%E2%80%9Cdue%20to%20the%20confidential%20and%20sensitive%20nature%20of%20proceedings%20of%20this%20case%E2%80%9D.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fqatar-court-commutes-death-sentence-given-to-eight-indian-navy-veterans%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Shivraj%20Chouhan%20No%20Longer%20In%20Charge%2C%20'Ladli%20Behnas'%20Wait%20For%20Gas%20Subsidies%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETwo%20months%20before%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20voted%2C%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20had%20promised%20at%20an%20event%20in%20Tikamgarh%20that%20the%20women%20of%20the%20state%20--%20he%20called%20them%20%26quot%3Bladli%20behna%26quot%3B%20after%20the%20scheme%20by%20that%20name%20--%20will%20get%20cooking%20gas%20cylinders%20for%20Rs%20450.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20conditions%20and%20eligibility%20criteria%2C%20of%20course%2C%20but%20the%20announcement%20was%20a%20big%20relief%20for%20households%2C%20especially%20those%20with%20many%20members.%20The%20announcement%20was%20also%20a%20political%20move%20by%20the%20BJP%20veteran%2C%20coming%20right%20after%20the%20Congress's%20promise%20to%20give%20out%20cooking%20gas%20cylinders%20for%20Rs%20500%20if%20it%20came%20to%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20month%20later%2C%20women%20in%20the%20state%20had%20reason%20to%20cheer.%20They%20bought%20a%20cooking%20gas%20cylinder%20for%20Rs%20910%20and%20received%20Rs%20460%20in%20their%20bank%20accounts%20soon%20after%20as%20subsidy.%20This%20meant%20they%20paid%20Rs%20450%20for%20the%20cylinder%2C%20in%20line%20with%20the%20then%20Chief%20Minister's%20promise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECut%20to%20the%20last%20week%20of%202023.%20The%20BJP%20has%20returned%20to%20power%2C%20but%20Mr%20Chouhan%20is%20not%20on%20the%20hot%20seat%20anymore.%20Mohan%20Yadav%20is%20the%20new%20Chief%20Minister%20as%20the%20BJP%20veteran%20waits%20for%20a%20new%20task.%20He%20is%20not%20alone.%20His%20%26quot%3Bladli%20behnas%26quot%3B%20are%20also%20waiting%2C%20for%20their%20subsidies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fpbqfhrao_shivraj-chouhan_625x300_04_December_23.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%2032%20lakh%20women%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20are%20registered%20for%20the%20cooking%20gas%20subsidy.%20One%20of%20them%20is%20Shashi%20Gawde%20from%20Bhopal's%20Bhimnagar%20neighbourhood.%20A%20beneficiary%20of%20the%20popular%20Ladli%20Behna%20scheme%2C%20she%20gets%20Rs%201%2C250%20in%20her%20bank%20account%20every%20month.%20The%20cooking%20gas%20subsidy%2C%20however%2C%20has%20stopped%20coming%2C%20she%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20Shivraj's%20announcement%2C%20we%20got%20the%20cylinder%20for%20Rs%20910%20and%20a%20subsidy%20of%20Rs%20460%20came%20into%20my%20account.%20But%20we%20did%20not%20receive%20it%20after%20that%20one%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20how%20long%20a%20cooking%20gas%20cylinder%20lasts%20for%20her%20family%2C%20she%20said%20there%20are%20many%20members%20and%20the%20cylinder%20runs%20out%20within%20a%20month.%20Not%20getting%20the%20subsidy%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Blot%20of%20trouble%26quot%3B%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPoonam%2C%20a%20labourer%2C%20is%20worried%20too.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20not%20getting%20anything%20now.%20Maybe%20they%20pay%20later%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BSometimes%20we%20don't%20have%20money%20to%20get%20a%20cylinder.%20We%20manage%20by%20borrowing%20money.%20All%20we%20earn%20is%20spent%20on%20our%20children's%20education.%20It's%20difficult%20to%20buy%20a%20cylinder%20for%20Rs%20910.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProviding%20cooking%20gas%20cylinders%20for%20Rs%20450%20to%20beneficiaries%20of%20the%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20government's%20Ujjwala%20Yojana%20and%20Laadli%20Behna%20scheme%20was%20part%20of%20the%20BJP's%20list%20of%20promises%20ahead%20of%20the%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Krishna%20Gaur%2C%20a%20minister%20in%20the%20new%20government%2C%20was%20asked%20about%20the%20pause%20in%20subsidies%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Chief%20Minister%20has%20already%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20our%20Sankalp%20Patra%20is%20as%20sacred%20to%20as%20Gita%20and%20Ramayana.%20Whatever%20promises%20we%20have%20made%20will%20be%20fulfilled.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20complaints%20of%20not%20receiving%20cooking%20gas%20subsidies%20also%20play%20out%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20massive%20debt%20burden%20on%20the%20state%20government.%20Less%20than%20two%20weeks%20after%20swearing-in%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Y