20the%20chief%20executive%20assistant%20to%20former%20Cisco%20CEO%20John%20Chambers.%20Gross%20joined%20Cisco%20in%201991%20when%20Chambers%20was%20a%20senior%20vice%20president%20and%20stayed%20in%20her%20position%20until%202017%2C%20just%20two%20years%20after%20Chambers%20stepped%20down%20as%20CEO.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGross%20was%2035%20when%20she%20joined%2C%20and%20earned%20a%20%2436%2C000%20salary%20at%20the%20company%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2014%2F12%2F19%2Fwhere-would-cisco-and-its-ceo-be-without-her.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ECNBC%20reported%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20Gross'%20many%20responsibilities%20was%20making%20sure%20Chambers%20was%20prepared%20for%20every%20meeting%2C%20conference%2C%20event%20or%20sales%20pitch%20by%20providing%20him%20with%20all%20the%20details%20needed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou'd%20be%20nauseated%20to%20see%20what%20we%20put%20together%20for%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20Gross%20told%20CNBC.%20%26quot%3BHe%20doesn't%20really%20know%20what%20he's%20doing%20until%20he%20goes%20on%20the%20plane.%20Our%20teams%20are%20constantly%20putting%20together%20materials%20for%20him%20to%20review.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChambers%20said%20about%20Gross%20in%20an%20email%20to%20CNBC%3A%20%26quot%3BDebbie%20has%20always%20been%20and%20continues%20to%20be%20a%20true%20business%20partner%3B%20she%20makes%20it%20a%20point%20to%20know%20the%20business%2C%20what%20my%20priorities%20are%20and%20she%20has%20the%20ability%20to%20represent%20me%20as%20well%20as%20Cisco%20in%20the%20absolute%20best%20professional%20manner.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20leaving%20Cisco%2C%20she's%20worked%20as%20a%20corporate%20trainer%20and%20a%20coach%20for%20people%20working%20in%20administration%2C%20according%20to%20her%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdebbiegross.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ewebsite%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20She%20also%20wrote%20%26quot%3BT