ease%20in%20seats%20and%20vote%20share%2C%20for%20example%2C%20can%20strengthen%20Congress%20over%20the%20next%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20many%20seats%20the%20Congress%20wins%20will%20also%20be%20important%20for%20maintaining%20a%20democratic%20balance%20in%20our%20polity.%20Every%20seat%20and%20every%20vote%20counts.%20The%20Congress%2C%20therefore%2C%20has%20to%20fight%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20with%20the%20confidence%20and%20gusto%20of%20a%20party%20that%20is%20in%20it%20to%20win.%20That%20is%20why%20%26quot%3BTayyar%20Hai%20Hum%26quot%3B%20is%20the%20right%20call%2C%20and%20along%20with%20the%20crowdfunding%20campaign%2C%20the%20party%20is%20sending%20the%20right%20signals%20to%20its%20workers%20and%20supporters%20-%20that%20it%20is%20up%20for%20the%20challenge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bharat%20Nyay%20Yatra%20is%20important%20for%20several%20reasons%2C%20not%20least%20that%20it%20will%20seek%20to%20improve%20the%20Congress's%20national%20appeal%2C%20raising%20its%20stakes%20in%20a%20national%20election.%20If%20confidence%20is%20half%20the%20battle%20won%2C%20the%20other%20half%20needs%20a%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20some%20suggestions%20for%20Congress%20to%20maximise%20its%20performance%20in%20the%202024%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1.%20Don't%20put%20all%20eggs%20in%20the%20INDIA%20basket%3A%20In%20public%20perception%2C%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20must%20be%20only%20one%20part%20of%20the%20Congress%20election%20strategy%20and%20campaign.%20The%20Congress%20will%20need%20to%20assert%20its%20own%20independent%20identity%20as%20well.%20The%20Bharat%20Nyay%20Yatra%20will%20help%20with%20this.%20The%20stronger%20the%20Congress%20looks%2C%20the%20stronger%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20will%20look.%20The%20bloc%20is%20important%20and%20useful%20but%20cannot%20be%20all-important%20for%20the%20Congress%2C%20not%20least%20because%20of%20the%20risk%20that%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20sometimes%20looks%20slow%20to%20move%2C%20and%20full%20of%20disagreement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2.%20Immediate%20focus%20on%20the%20narrative.%20With%20just%20about%20three%20months%20to%20go%20for%20the%20national%20election%2C%20the%20Congress%20must%20immediately%20make%20its%20narrative%20clear%2C%20as%20also%20its%20programme%2C%20its%20promises%2C%20guarantees%2C%20vision%2C%20and%20agenda%20for%20the%20people%20of%20India.%20While%20a%20manifesto%20committee%20has%20been%20formed%2C%20there%20isn't%20enough%20time%20to%20wait%20for%20one.%20Remember%2C%20the%20last-hour%20launch%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BNYAY%26quot%3B%20campaign%20hardly%20helped%20in%202019.%20The%20same%20mistake%20should%20not%20be%20made%20again.%20The%20key%20promises%2C%20the%20slogan%2C%20and%20the%20narrative%20of%20the%20Congress%20party's%202024%20election%20campaign%20must%20be%20decided%20and%20announced%20as%20soon%20as%20possible.%20Getting%20the%20message%20across%20to%20the%20masses%20takes%20far%20longer%20than%20most%20presume.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3.%20Focus%20on%20jobs.%20The%20Bharat%20Nyay%20Yatra%2C%20with%20its%20focus%20on%20justice%2C%20must%20talk%20about%20the%20injustice%20of%20unemployment%20as%20the%20main%20issue.%20That%20is%20the%20number%20one%20issue%20today.%20There%20should%20be%20mass%20mobilisation%20of%20unemployed%20youth%20for%20a%20new%20economic%20agenda%20that%20will%20focus%20on%20creating%20jobs.%20As%20survey%20after%20survey%20shows%20this%20to%20be%20a%20major%20concern%2C%20this%20is%20low-hanging%20fruit%20for%20Congress.%20Unemployed%20youth%20can%20add%20a%20few%20percentage%20points%20to%20the%20Congress's%20vote%20share.%20More%20importantly%2C%20they%20can%20become%20amplifiers%20of%20the%20Congress's%20voice%20in%20society.%20A%20targeted%2C%20concerted%20focus%20on%20unemployment%20is%20a%20must.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E4.%20Focus%20on%20inequality%3A%20India%20is%20one%20of%20the%20fastest-growing%20world%20economies%2C%20but%20there%20is%20enough%20data%20to%20show%20that%20the%20bottom%20half%20isn't%20climbing%20up%20the%20economic%20ladder.%20If%20the%20government%20has%20had%20to%20increase%20the%20NREGA%20budget%20and%20give%20free%20food%20grains%20to%2080%20crore%20people%2C%20it%20is%20proof%20that%20the%20poor%20aren't%20getting%20the%20leg-up%20they%20should.%20It%20is%20time%20to%20ask%20the%202004%20question%20again%3A%20Aam%20Aadmi%20ko%20kya%20mila%3F%20While%20jobs%20can%20be%20the%20specific%20issue%2C%20the%20larger%20question%20about%20economic%20inequality%20must%20be%20in%20focus.%20The%20Bharat%20Nyay%20Yatra%20must%20focus%20on%20economic%20injustice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E5.%20Recharge%20the%20party%20organisation.%20It%20is%20the%20party%20worker%20who%20gets%20the%20vote%20out%20on%20polling%20day.%20The%20party%20must%20enthuse%20the%20worker%2C%20especially%20as%20the%20worker%20is%20demoralised%20today.%20The%20Bharat%20Nyay%20Yatra%20must%20address%20workers%20every%20morning%20before%20it%20addresses%20the%20common%20public.%20Steps%20must%20be%20taken%20to%20show%20that%20the%20Congress%20party%20values%20and%20respects%20the%20contribution%20of%20workers.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20technology%20must%20be%20used%20to%20determine%20how%20many%20workers%20are%20actually%20active%20-%20how%20many%20are%20willing%20to%20execute%20simple%20door-to-door%20campaign%20tasks%20such%20as%20securing%20donations%20or%20signatures%20on%20petitions.%20Some%20would%20say%20it's%20not%20the%20right%20time%20for%20a%20new%20membership%20drive%20-%20but%20then%2C%20a%20membership%20drive%20should%20be%20a%20365-day%20affair%20anyway.%20The%20more%20new%20members%20join%20Congress%20at%20election%20time%2C%20the%20more%20their%20neighbours%2C%20friends%2C%20and%20family%20take%20the%20party%20seriously.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E6.%20Turn%20supporters%20into%20online%20amplifiers%3A%20We%20now%20live%20in%20the%20social%20media%20age.%20The%20dense%20penetration%20of%20smartphones%20must%20be%20used%20better%20for%20political%20campaigning.%20