ut%20her%20marriage%20to%20boyfriend%20Shantanu%20Hazarika%2C%20which%20surfaced%20after%20Orhan%20Awatramani%20referred%20to%20him%20as%20her%20husband.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tejashree%20Bhopatkar%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22China%20could%20take%20steps%20to%20prop%20up%20its%20economy%2C%20but%20that%20would%20leave%20it%20vulnerable%20to%20a%20'Lehman%20moment%2C'%20economist%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22beijing%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6581c7d6cefc010bea24f441%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221750%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPeople%20cross%20a%20street%20in%20the%20technology%20district%20of%20Shenzhen%2C%20China%20September%2014%2C%202015.%3Cp%3EREUTERS%2FBobby%20Yip%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Conference%20Board%20forecasts%20China's%20GDP%20growth%20in%202024%20to%20decelerate%20to%204.1%25.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWhile%20Beijing%20has%20the%20capacity%20to%20engineer%20stronger%20growth%2C%20doing%20so%20could%20risk%20worsening%20structural%20issues.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELarge%20stimulus%20could%20provide%20a%20near-term%20boost%2C%20but%20may%20open%20the%20door%20to%20a%20%26quot%3BLehman%20moment%26quot%3B%20later%20on.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EChina's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-economy-deflation-markets-property-real-estate-housing-beijing-2023-8%5C%22%3Epost-pandemic%20rebound%3C%2Fa%3E%20failed%20to%20materialize%20this%20year%2C%20and%20it's%20unlikely%20to%20arrive%20in%202024%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Conference%20Board.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-economy-beijing-lehman-moment-policy-deflation-economy-markets-property-2023-8%5C%22%3Ewobbling%20property%20sector%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20declining%20domestic%20demand%2C%20waning%20foreign%20investment%2C%20and%20deteriorating%20consumer%20confidence%20all%20pose%20headwinds%20to%20the%20world's%20second%20largest%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlfredo%20Montufar-Helu%2C%20the%20head%20of%20the%20Conference%20Board's%20China%20Center%20for%20Economics%20and%20Business%2C%20said%20policymakers%20have%20the%20ability%20to%20spark%20a%20near-term%20boost%20via%20stimulus%2C%20but%20doing%20so%20would%20open%20the%20door%20to%20worsening%20long-term%20impacts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20massive%20stimulus%20would%20perhaps%20lead%20to%20a%20number%20of%20years%20of%20good%20growth%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BBut%20once%20the%20effect%20of%20the%20stimulus%20dissipates%2C%20China%20would%20be%20left%20with%20a%20bigger%20problem%2C%20and%20then%20we%20would%20really%20have%20to%20consider%20whether%20there%20is%20a%20possibility%20for%20a%20Chinese%20'Lehman%20moment.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20broad-based%20stimulus%20plan%20would%20extend%20debt%20maturities%2C%20but%20when%20they%20come%20due%2C%20it%20could%20trigger%20more%20defaults%20that%20set%20off%20a%20domino%20effect%20in%20financial%20markets%20and%20lead%20to%20a%20liquidity%20crunch%2C%20Montufar-Helu%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20government%20would%20have%20less%20capacity%20to%20respond%20because%20of%20the%20magnitude%20of%20the%20problem%20and%20because%20the%20previous%20stimulus%20would%20have%20likely%20strained%20its%20fiscal%20and%20financial%20capacities%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20economist%20said%20policymakers%20appear%20to%20be%20moving%20cautiously%20with%20moderate%20and%20targeted%20fiscal%20interventions%20over%20recent%20months.%20In%20fact%2C%20nothing%20has%20come%20close%20to%20the%20stimulus%20package%20that%20came%20during%20the%20Great%20Financial%20Crisis%2C%20which%20led%20to%20some%20of%20the%20current%20structural%20issues%20China%20faces%20today.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20China%20must%20find%20a%20way%20to%20reduce%20its%20people's%20need%20for%20precautionary%20savings.%20Building%20a%20social%20safety%20net%20won't%20happen%20in%20one%20or%20two%20years%2C%20he%20said%2C%20but%20working%20toward%20that%20will%20allow%20for%20a%20consumer-%20and%20demand-drive%20economic%20model.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20coming%20years%20could%20bring%20a%20prolonged%20period%20of%20below-potential%20growth%20as%20Beijing%20works%20through%20its%20structural%20imbalances.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20this%20is%20necessary%2C%26quot%3B%20Montufar-Helu%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20alternative%20is%20the%20implementation%20of%20a%20massive%20stimulus%20plan%20that%20would%20only%20exacerbate%20structural%20imbalances%20and%20kick%20the%20can%20down%20the%20road.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-economy-outlook-beijing-real-estate-markets-ehman-2024-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703761501000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6581c7f61c5c7b8c9a09b6a9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-economy-outlook-beijing-real-estate-markets-ehman-2024-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chinese%20policymakers%20have%20the%20ability%20to%20engineer%20stronger%20growth%2C%20but%20that%20may%20worsen%20the%20structural%20issues%20that%20have%20hampered%20the%20economy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22prosen%40insider.com%20(Phil%20Rosen)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-economy-outlook-beijing-real-estate-markets-ehman-2024-2023-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Musk's%20latest%20threat%20from%20China%20is%20a%20new%20luxury%20EV%20built%20by%20one%20of%20its%20biggest%20smartphone%20firms%22%2C%22co