0that%20day.%20I'd%20think%20%26quot%3BWell%2C%20that's%20cool.%26quot%3B%20But%20when%20the%20next%20day%20comes%2C%20I%20go%20back%20to%20my%20life%20like%20nothing%20has%20changed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20after%20getting%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-a-weekend-is-like-yale-student-campus-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cmark%20data-color%3D%5C%22%23fef586%5C%22%3Eaccepted%20to%20Yale%3C%2Fmark%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20my%20dream%20school%2C%20I%20had%20to%20go%20through%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fa-step-by-step-guide-to-securing-a-big-law-summer-associate-position-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cmark%20data-color%3D%5C%22%23fef586%5C%22%3Erecruiting%20for%20a%20law%20firm%3C%2Fmark%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20after%20that%2C%20applying%20for%20clerkships.%20I%20realized%20in%20the%20end%20that%20I%20would%20never%20be%20fulfilled%20even%20as%20an%20equity%20partner%20because%20once%20I%20made%20it%2C%20I%20would%20become%20obsessed%20with%20the%20next%20goal%20%E2%80%94%20there's%20always%20the%3Cem%3E%20next%20%3C%2Fem%3Ething%20I%20think%20I%20need%20to%20do%2C%20and%20I%20never%20reached%20a%20point%20where%20I%20thought%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20so%20happy%3B%20this%20is%20my%20dream.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20happiness%20I%20felt%20was%20so%20fleeting%2C%20and%20I%20quickly%20forgot%20it%20and%20returned%20to%20feeling%20dissatisfied.%20Sometimes%2C%20I%20wondered%20why%20I%20still%20felt%20lonely%20and%20even%20cried%20every%20day%20after%20getting%20what%20I%20wanted%20for%20so%20long.%20Then%2C%20I%20realized%20I%20wasn't%20tired%20of%20chasing%20goals%20%E2%80%94%20I%20was%20just%20weirded%20out%20by%20how%20unfulfilling%20they%20were.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20unfulfilled%20feeling%20propels%20me%20to%20chase%20prestige%20as%20a%20way%20for%20me%20to%20seek%20happiness.%20But%20somewhere%20along%20the%20way%2C%20while%20chasing%20prestige%2C%20I%20was%2