Claims%20His%20Wife%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPolice%20here%20have%20lodged%20an%20FIR%20after%20a%20revenue%20officer's%20wife%20alleged%20that%20he%20was%20forcibly%20converted%20to%20Islam%20and%20made%20to%20marry%20a%20Muslim%20woman%2C%20officials%20said%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArti%20Gupta%20went%20to%20the%20police%20when%20she%20learnt%20about%20the%20%26quot%3Bwedding%26quot%3B%20through%20social%20media%20as%20her%20husband%20Ashish%20Kumar%20Gupta%20--%20a%20naib%20tehsildar%20posted%20in%20Maudaha%20tehsil%20of%20Hamirpur%20--%20had%20not%20come%20home%20for%20almost%20four%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20police%2C%20Ashish%20Kumar%20Gupta%20has%20so%20far%20not%20been%20traced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20complaint%20lodged%20at%20the%20City%20Kotwali%20Police%20Station%2C%20Arti%20Gupta%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Kanpur%20city%2C%20said%20her%20husband%20was%20%26quot%3Bforcibly%26quot%3B%20converted%20to%20Islam%20and%20made%20to%20marry%20a%20Muslim%20woman%20named%20Rukhsaar%2C%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20a%20case%20was%20registered%20against%20five%20people%2C%20including%20the%20Naib%20Tehsildar%2C%20and%20around%20six%20unidentified%20people.%20Two%20of%20them%2C%20including%20a%20maulvi%20at%20a%20local%20masque%20in%20Maudaha%2C%20have%20been%20detained%2C%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArti%20Gupta%20told%20police%20that%20her%20husband%20was%20having%20an%20affair%20with%20Rukhsaar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERukhsar's%20father%2C%20one%20Munna%2C%20Maulvi%20Babu%20Aadhati%20of%20a%20local%20mosque%20in%20Maudaha%20and%20four%20to%20five%20others%20%26quot%3Bforcibly%26quot%3B%20converted%20Ashish%20Gupta%20on%20December%2024%20and%20got%20him%20married%20to%20the%20woman%2C%20she%20alleged%20in%20the%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20said%20a%20case%20has%20been%20registered%20against%20Ashish%20Gupta%2C%20Rukhsaar%2C%20her%20father%2C%20Munna%2C%20Aadhati%20and%20five%20to%20six%20unidentified%20people%20under%20section%20494%20(marrying%20again%20during%20lifetime%20of%20husband%20or%20wife)%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20and%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Prohibition%20of%20Unlawful%20Conversion%20of%20Religion%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20registering%20the%20case%2C%20the%20accused%20maulvi%20and%20Munna%20have%20been%20taken%20into%20custody%20and%20are%20being%20interrogated%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20some%20locals%2C%20Ashish%20Gupta%20would%20also%20offer%20namaz%20in%20a%20mosque%20in%20Maudaha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20caretaker%20of%20the%20mosque%2C%20Muhammad%20Mushtaq%2C%20said%20Ashish%20Gupta%20identified%20himself%20as%20Mohammad%20Yusuf.%20Later%2C%20when%20he%20revealed%20that%20he%20was%20the%20naib%20tehsildar%20of%20Maudaha%20and%20a%20resident%20of%20Kanpur%2C%20the%20caretaker%20informed%20the%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaudaha%20Tehsildar%20Balram%20Gupta%2C%20however%2C%20said%20the%20reports%20of%20the%20naib%20tehsildar%20offering%20namaz%20could%20not%20be%20verified.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statements%20of%20local%20people%20in%20Maudaha%20were%20recorded%20as%20part%20of%20the%20investigation.%20The%20claims%20of%20Ashish%20Gupta%20offering%20namaz%20in%20a%20mosque%20could%20not%20be%20verified%2C%20Balram%20Gupta%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703751420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-12%2F9u60msi_indian-wedding-generic_625x300_04_December_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fup-man-forcibly-converted-made-to-marry-muslim-woman-claims-his-wife-4756867%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Police%20here%20have%20lodged%20an%20FIR%20after%20a%20revenue%20officer's%20wife%20alleged%20that%20he%20was%20forcibly%20converted%20t