0Party%E2%80%99s%20Storm%20Troopers%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGovernors%20sitting%20on%20Bills%20stifle%20law-making%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20rather%20extraordinary%20that%20while%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fparliament-proceedings-three-more-opposition-mps-suspended-as-protest-over-mass-suspension-continues%2Farticle67661514.ece%5C%22%3E146%20MPs%20from%20the%20opposition%20parties%20have%20been%20suspended%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20both%20Houses%20of%20parliament%2C%20governments%20formed%20by%20opposition%20parties%20in%20several%20states%20are%20being%20checkmated%20by%20governors%20who%2C%20as%20appointees%20of%20the%20Union%20government%2C%20are%20stifling%20their%20legislative%20apparatus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnelected%20governors%20have%20no%20authority%20to%20impede%20the%20functioning%20of%20elected%20legislatures.%20When%20a%20governor%20refers%20a%20Bill%20to%20the%20president%2C%20the%20Bill%20is%20actually%20referred%20to%20the%20government%20of%20India.%20Those%20Bills%20are%20not%20directly%20sent%20to%20the%20president%20by%20the%20governor.%20They%20are%20sent%20to%20the%20Union%20home%20ministry%2C%20which%20examines%20them%20after%20getting%20advice%20from%20concerned%20ministries%20of%20the%20government%20of%20India%2C%20and%20submits%20them%20to%20the%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20those%20Bills%20passed%20by%20the%20state%20legislature%20and%20embodying%20the%20legislative%20intent%20of%20that%20assembly%20get%20subordinated%20to%20the%20intent%20of%20the%20Union%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20case%20the%20president%2C%20acting%20on%20the%20advice%20of%20the%20government%2C%20does%20not%20give%20her%2Fhis%20assent%2C%20then%20those%20Bills%20are%20dead.%20It%20is%20quite%20possible%20that%20the%20seven%20Bills%20from%20Kerala%20would%20meet%20such%20a%20fate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERecommendations%20of%20the%20Sarkaria%20Commission%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Sarkaria%20Commission%20report%20on%20Centre-state%20relations%2C%20and%20its%20observations%20and%20recommendations%20contained%20in%20a%20separate%20chapter%20titled%20%E2%80%9CReservation%20of%20Bills%20by%20Governors%20for%20President%E2%80%99s%20Consideration%20and%20Promulgation%20of%20Ordinances%E2%80%9D%2C%20are%20of%20great%20relevance%20in%20this%20context.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20invoked%20the%20study%20team%20of%20the%20administrative%20reforms%20commission%2C%20which%20had%20noted%20that%20the%20reservation%20of%20a%20large%20number%20of%20Bills%20by%20governors%20for%20presidential%20consideration%20would%20be%20%E2%80%9Ccontrary%20to%20the%20federal%20spirit%20of%20the%20constitution%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Farif-mohammed-khan-pinarayi-vijayan-kerala%5C%22%3EIn%20Arif%20Mohammed%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20Steadfast%20Opposition%20to%20Kerala%20Govt%2C%20a%20Hint%20of%20His%20Usual%20Politics%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Commission%20observed%20that%20such%20powers%20%E2%80%9Care%20intended%20to%20subserve%20the%20broad%20purpose%20of%20cooperative%20federalism%20in%20the%20realm%20of%20Union-state%20legislative%20relations%E2%80%9D%20and%20when%20%E2%80%9Cused%20sparingly%20in%20proper%20cases%2C%20e.g.%20where%20the%20Bill%20relates%20to%20a%20matter%20falling%20clearly%20within%20the%20Union%20List%2C%20it%20serves%20a%20useful%20purpose%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20then%20quoted%20constitutional%20expert%20D.D.%20Basu%2C%20who%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20powers%20of%20governors%20to%20refer%20Bills%20to%20the%20president%2C%20had%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6its%20use%20cannot%20be%20extended%20to%20such%20an%20extent%20as%20to%20install%20the%20Union%20executive%20over%20the%20head%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20legislature%20in%20matters%20legislative.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Commission%20recommended%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cneedless%20reservation%20of%20Bills%20for%20%5Bthe%5D%20president%E2%80%99s%20consideration%20should%20be%20avoided%E2%80%9D.%20It%20is%20instructive%20to%20note%20that%20it%20recommended%2C%20%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20matter%20of%20salutary%20convention%2C%20a%20reference%20should%20be%20disposed%20of%20by%20the%20president%20within%20a%20period%20of%20four%20months%20from%20the%20date%20on%20which%20the%20reference%20is%20received%20by%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20example%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20was%20prime%20minister%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20chief%20minister%20Digvijaya%20Singh%20requested%20him%20to%20expeditiously%20take%20a%20decision%20on%20three%20Bills%20passed%20by%20the%20state%20assembly%20and%20referred%20to%20the%20president%20by%20the%20governor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20president%20gave%20his%20assent%20in%20three%20months.%20It%20demonstrated%20how%2C%20through%20deliberation%20and%20consultation%2C%20the%20constitutional%20scheme%20of%20governance%20could%20be%20adopted%20effectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20example%20and%20those%20utterances%20of%20the%20Commission%20assume%20greater%20significance%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EConstitutional%20role%20of%20governors%20and%20unity%20and%20integrity%20of%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20separate%20chapter%20on%20the%20%E2%80%98Role%20of%20Governors%E2%80%99%2C%20the%20Sarkaria%20Commission%20observed%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20part%20which%20the%20governor%20plays%20to%20help%20maintain%20the%20democratic%20form%20of%20government%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20constitution%20is%20of%20vital%20importance%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20ultimate%20analysis%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20remarked%2C%20%E2%80%9Cdue%20observance%20of%20the%20constitutional%20provisions%20is%20the%20soundest%20guarantee%20of%20enduring%20unity%20and%20integrity%20of%20the%20nation%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20manner%20in%20which%20the%20governors%20in%20most%20opposition-run%20states%20act%20in%20impeding%20the%20legislative%20functioning%20of%20elected%20assemblies%20raises%20questions%20about%20their%20actions%20to%20safeguard%20our%20unity%20and%20integrity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fs-n-sahu%5C%22%3ES.N.%20Sahu%3C%2Fa%3E%20served%20as%20officer%20on%20special%20duty%20to%20President%20K.R.%20Narayan.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703749585000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F03132819%2FF7m7Y5YaIAAeDNr.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fkerala-governor-withholding-assent-bills%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Sarkaria%20Commission%20report%20on%20Centre-state%20relations%20observed%20that%20a%20governor's%20power%20to%20reserve%20Bills%20for%20presidential%20consideration%20must%20be%20%E2%80%9Cused%20sparingly%E2%80%9D%20and%20in%20limited%20contexts%2C%20adding%20that%20reserving%20a%20large%20number%20of%20Bills%20would%20be%20contrary%20to%20the%20constitution's%20federal%20spirit.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fkerala-governor-withholding-assent-bills%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Season%202%20of%20'Guns%20%26amp%3B%20Gulaabs'%20announced%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703749501000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106344758%2Cimgsize-49810.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fhindi%2Fseason-2-of-rajkummar-raos-guns-gulaabs-announced%2Farticleshow%2F106344656.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F106344656.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20year%202023%20saw%20numerous%20OTT%20releases%2C%20including%20Raj%20and%20DK's%20'Guns%20%26amp%3B%20Gulaabs'%2C%20a%20black%20comedy%20crime%20thriller%20featuring%20Rajkummar%20Rao%2C%20Dulquer%20Salmaan%2C%20Gulshan%20Devaish%2C%20Adarsh%20Gourav%2C%20and%20more.%20The%20series%20received%20praise%20from%20critics%20and%20audiences%20alike%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20announcement%20of%20its%20sequel.%20The%20streaming%20platform%20unveiled%20the%20news%20of%20'Guns%20%26amp%3B%20Gulaabs'%20Season%202%20through%20a%20video%20showcasing%20the%20returning%20cast.%20While%20the%20release%20date%20is%20unknown%2C%20filming%20is%20expected%20to%20begin%20in%202024.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fhindi%2Fseason-2-of-rajkummar-raos-guns-gulaabs-announced%2Farticleshow%2F106344656.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Flight%20Affected%20Due%20To%20Fog%3F%20Know%20Your%20Rights%20As%20A%20Passenger%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAir%20India%20has%20recently%20introduced%20the%20%26quot%3BFog%20Care%26quot%3B%20initiative%2C%20offering%20a%20solution%20for%20passengers%20who%20may%20face%20delays%20due%20to%20fog.%20This%20program%20allows%20affected%20passengers%20to%20reschedule%20or%20cancel%20their%20flights%20without%20any%20additional%20charges.%20When%20your%20flight%20is%20affected%20due%20to%20fog%20or%20other%20weather-related%20issues%2C%20it%20is%20essential%20to%20be%20aware%20of%20your%20rights%20as%20a%20passenger.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere%20are%20some%20general%20guidelines%20that%20may%20apply%2C%20but%20specific%20policies%20can%20vary%20between%20airlines%20and%20regions%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EFlight%20Cancellations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%C2%A0Airlines%20are%20usually%20required%20to%20offer%20passengers%20alternative%20flights%20or%20provide%20a%20refund%20for%20the%20affected%20portion%20of%20the%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECommunication%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%C2%A0Airlines%20are%20expected%20to%20keep%20passengers%20informed%20about%20the%20status%20of%20their%20flights.%20This%20includes%20updates%20on%20delays%2C%20cancellations%2C%20and%20alternative%20arrangements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ERebooking%20and%20Refunds%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%C2%A0Passengers%20affected%20by%20fog-related%20disruptions%20may%20be%20eligible%20to%20rebook%20on%20the%20next%20available%20flight%20without%20extra%20charges%20or%2C%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20a%20refund%20for%20the%20affected%20leg%20of%20the%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ETravel%20Insurance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%C2%A0Check%20your%20travel%20insurance%20policy%2C%20as%20it%20may%20provide%20coverage%20for%20certain%20expenses%20incurred%20due%20to%20flight%20delays%20or%20cancellations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECheck%20Airline%20Policies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%C2%A0Airlines%20have%20specific%20policies%20regarding%20weather-related%20disruptions%2C%20and%20these%20can%20vary.%20It%20is%20advisable%20to%20check%20the%20terms%20and%20conditions%20of%20your%20airline%20to%20understand%20your%20rights%20and%20the%20compensation%20or%20assistance%20they%20provide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlternate%20Transportation%20and%20Accommodation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%C2%A0Airlines%20may%20provide%20accommodation%20and%20alternative%20transportation%20options%20for%20significant%20delays%20or%20cancellations%20due%20to%20fog.%20Check%20with%20the%20airline%20for%20details%20on%20their%20policies%20in%20such%20situations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%20cases%20of%20connecting%20flights%20affected%20by%20fog%20at%20the%20starting%20location%2C%20you%20can%20try%20rescheduling%20online%20or%20at%20the%20airport.%20Just%20ask%20your%20airline%20for%20help.%20For%20those%20considering%20cancelling%20a%20booking%20due%20to%20prolonged%20delays%20and%20seeking%20a%20refund%2C%20a%20strategic%20approach%20involves%20choosing%20refundable%20tickets.%20Keeping%20an%20eye%20on%20recent%20air%20travel%20and%20weather%20trends%20in%20the%20region%20can%20help%20passengers%20anticipate%20potential%20delays.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAlaska%20Airlines%20offers%20flexibility%20to%20passengers%20facing%20fog-related%20flight%20delays%20by%20allowing%20them%20to%20reschedule%20without%20additional%20charges.%20However%2C%20no%20specific%20laws%20mandate%20airlines%20to%20provide%20monetary%20compensation%20for%20delays%20or%20cancellations%20due%20to%20fog.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703748480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-12%2F8dlge7l8_delhi-airport-t3-departure-pti-december-2022-650_650x400_15_December_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fflight-affected-due-to-fog-know-your-rights-as-a-passenger-4756599%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Air%20India's%20%26quot%3BFog%20Care%26quot%3B%20initiative%20sends%20app%20notifications%20to%20passengers%2C%20advising%20them%20to%20reschedule%20their%20flights%20in%20case%20of%20predicted%20fog%20situations.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fflight-affected-due-to-fog-know-your-rights-as-a-passenger-4756599%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fflight-affected-due-to-fog-know-your-rights-as-a-passenger-4756599%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fflight-affected-due-to-fog-know-your-rights-as-a-passenger-4756599%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%222024%20Travel