%20accusing%20the%20retired%20IPS%20officer%20of%20displaying%20%E2%80%9Cdeep%20political%20bias.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20state%20unit%20released%20a%20statement%20on%20Wednesday%20expressing%20%E2%80%9Cprofound%20disappointment%20and%20concern%E2%80%9D%20over%20Ribeiro%E2%80%99s%20remarks.%20At%20the%20event%20in%20question%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20Ribeiro%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CHindus%20and%20Christians%20in%20Pakistan%20are%20living%20in%20fear%20as%20second-class%20citizens%E2%80%A6%20that%20may%20happen%20here%20%5Bin%20India%5D.%20This%20is%20what%20I%20fear%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fformer-mumbai-top-cop-comments-minorities-bjp-fire-goa-9085409%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20recent%20interaction%20with%20members%20of%20the%20Christian%20community%20in%20Delhi%20on%20Christmas%2C%20Ribeiro%20suggested%20that%20Modi%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fformer-mumbai-top-cop-comments-minorities-bjp-fire-goa-9085409%2F%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Ctrying%20to%20woo%20a%20big%20Christian%20community%20in%20Kerala.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20He%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9COne%20of%20the%20bishops%20has%20fallen%20for%20it.%20I%20feel%20because%20one%20has%20fallen%2C%20others%20perhaps%20may%20also%20fall.%20Let%E2%80%99s%20see%20what%20he%20(Modi)%20is%20trying%20to%20do.%20Even%20among%20our%20friends%2C%20they%20have%20started%20understanding%20that%20many%20of%20the%20things%20he%20said%20were%20only%20for%20votes.%20It%20is%20hoped%20that%20his%20Christmas%20message%20is%20probably%20a%20change%20of%20heart.%20If%20it%20is%2C%20it%20will%20be%20a%20good%20thing.%20But%20I%20doubt%20it%2C%20since%20the%20whole%20intention%20is%20to%20have%20a%20saffronised%20Pakistan.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20Giriraj%20Pai%20Vernekar%2C%20the%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20Goa%20BJP%2C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fformer-mumbai-top-cop-comments-minorities-bjp-fire-goa-9085409%2F%5C%22%3E%20criticised%20Ribeiro%E2%80%99s%20comparisons%20between%20India%20and%20Pakistan%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20describing%20them%20as%20%E2%80%9Cunfounded%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cdeeply%20offensive%20to%20the%20ethos%20and%20achievements%20of%20our%20great%20nation.%E2%80%9D%20Vernekar%20accused%20Ribeiro%20of%20harbouring%20%E2%80%9Cdeep%20hatred%20and%20frustration%20at%20having%20a%20government%20in%20power%20that%20possibly%20does%20not%20conform%20to%20his%20ideology.%E2%80%9D%20He%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CBut%2C%20to%20demean%20the%20country%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20belittle%20the%20government%20is%20unbecoming%20of%20a%20former%20cop.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERibeiro%20was%20the%20Commissioner%20of%20Mumbai%20Police%20from%201982%20to%201986%20and%20later%20held%20the%20post%20of%20Director%20General%20of%20Central%20Reserve%20Police%20Force%20and%20then%20Director%20General%20Police%20of%20Gujarat.%20He%20also%20served%20as%20Indian%20Ambassador%20to%20Romania%20from%201989%20until%201993.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703747349000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F28123436%2FCopy-of-Copy-of-Lead-image-size-4.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fbjp-accuses-former-top-cop-of-deep-bias-over-his-concerns-about-minority-rights%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BHindus%20and%20C