%2Fmiddle-east%2Fisraeli-embassy-pulls-video-imagining-hamas-attack-in-seoul%2Farticleshow%2F106342541.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F106342541.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20Israeli%20embassy%20in%20South%20Korea%20has%20removed%20a%20video%20showing%20an%20imaginary%20scenario%20in%20which%20Koreans%20are%20attacked%20by%20masked%20assailants%20in%20Seoul%2C%20a%20reference%20to%20Hamas%2C%20Seoul's%20foreign%20ministry%20said%20Thursday.%20The%20video%2C%20which%20is%20no%20longer%20available%20on%20the%20embassy's%20social%20media%2C%20depicted%20a%20distressing%20scenario%20in%20which%20a%20South%20Korean%20woman%20in%20the%20capital%20is%20abducted%20by%20an%20armed%20assailant%20on%20Christmas%20Day%2C%20and%20forcibly%20separated%20from%20her%20young%20daughter%2C%20a%20clip%20published%20by%20South%20Korean%20broadcaster%20YTN%20showed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fisraeli-embassy-pulls-video-imagining-hamas-attack-in-seoul%2Farticleshow%2F106342541.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fisraeli-embassy-pulls-video-imagining-hamas-attack-in-seoul%2Famp_articleshow%2F106342541.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fisraeli-embassy-pulls-video-imagining-hamas-attack-in-seoul%2Famp_articleshow%2F106342541.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ratan%20Tata%20Turns%2086%3A%2010%20Facts%20On%20India's%20'Most-Followed'%20Industrialist%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ERatan%20Naval%20Tata%20is%20the%20great-grandson%20of%20Jamsetji%20Tata%20who%20founded%20the%20Tata%20Group.%20He%20was%20born%20on%20December%2028%2C%201937%2C%20in%20Mumbai%20to%20Naval%20Tata%20and%20Sooni%20Tata.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHe%20was%20raised%20by%20his%20grandmother%2C%20Navajbai%20Tata%20after%20his%20parents%20separated%20in%201948.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDespite%20coming%20close%20to%20marriage%20on%20four%20occasions%2C%20Ratan%20Tata%20is%20still%20unmarried.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHe%20once%20admitted%20that%20he%20fell%20in%20love%20while%20working%20in%20Los%20Angeles.%20But%20because%20of%20the%20ongoing%201962%20Indo-China%20War%2C%20the%20girl's%20parents%20refused%20to%20let%20her%20move%20to%20India.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECommencing%20his%20career%20in%201961%2C%20Ratan%20Tata%20started%20from%20the%20ground%20up%2C%20managing%20operations%20on%20the%20shop%20floor%20of%20Tata%20Steel.%20This%20experience%20laid%20the%20foundation%20for%20his%20future%20leadership%20role%20within%20the%20group.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHe%20began%20restructuring%20the%20Tata%20group%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20liberalisation%20of%20the%20Indian%20economy%20was%20underway.%20He%20played%20an%20instrumental%20role%20in%20the%20business%20expansion%20of%20popular%20cars%20including%20the%20Tata%20Nano%20and%20Tata%20Indica.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHe%20got%20Tata%20Tea%20to%20acquire%20Tetley%2C%20Tata%20Motors%20to%20acquire%20Jaguar%20Land%20Rover%2C%20and%20Tata%20Steel%20to%20acquire%20Corus%20in%202004.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%202009%2C%20Ratan%20fulfilled%20his%20promise%20to%20make%20the%20world's%20cheapest%20car%20accessible%20to%20the%20middle%20class.%20The%20Tata%20Nano%2C%20priced%20at%20Rs%201%20lakh%2C%20became%20a%20symbol%20of%20innovation%20and%20affordability.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWith%20over%2012%20million%20followers%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%2C%20Ratan%20Tata%20is%20the%20'most%20followed%20entrepreneur'%20in%20the%20country%2C%20according%20to%20the%20360%20ONE%20Wealth%20Hurun%20India%20Rich%20List%202023.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EContinuing%20a%20tradition%20dating%20back%20to%20the%20time%20of%20Jamsetji%20Tata%2C%20Ratan%20Tata%20ensured%20that%20Bombay%20House%2C%20the%20Tata%20group's%20headquarters%2C%20remained%20a%20haven%20for%20stray%20dogs.%20The%20recently%20renovated%20Bombay%20House%20includes%20a%20dedicated%20kennel%20with%20provisions%20for%20food%2C%20water%2C%20toys%2C%20and%20a%20play%20area%2C%20embodying%20his%20compassion%20for%20animals.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703745720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fk7v5t9vs_ratan-tata_625x300_28_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fratan-tata-turns-86-10-interesting-facts-on-indias-most-followed-industrialist-4756404%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ratan%20Tata%2C%20one%20of%20India's%20most%20respected%20businessmen%2C%20turned%2086%20today.%20The%20Tata%20Sons%20Chairman%20is%20known%20not%20just%20for%20his%20contributions%20to%20the%20business%20world%2C%20but%20also%20his%20philanthropic%20activities.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fratan-tata-turns-86-10-interesting-facts-on-indias-most-followed-industrialist-4756404%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fratan-tata-turns-86-10-interesting-facts-on-indias-most-followed-industrialist-4756404%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fratan-tata-turns-86-10-interesting-facts-on-indias-most-followed-industrialist-4756404%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ahan-Sajid%20to%20team%20up%20again%20after%20Tadap%3A%20Excl%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703745235000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106342015%2Cimgsize-31982.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fahan-shetty-and-sajid-nadiadwala-to-team-up-again-after-tadap-leading-bollywood-actress-being-considered-for-the-same-exclusiv