oals%5C%22%3EBharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20Kanyakumari%20to%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20time%2C%20the%20yatra%20will%20start%20from%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20capital%2C%20Imphal%2C%20and%20end%20in%20Mumbai.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAddressing%20the%20media%20on%20December%2026%2C%20Congress%20general%20secretary%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20organisation%2C%20K.C.%20Venugopal%2C%20the%20Bharat%20Nyay%20Yatra%20will%20cover%20Manipur%2C%20Nagaland%2C%20Assam%2C%20Meghalaya%2C%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Bihar%2C%20Jharkhand%2C%20Odisha%2C%C2%A0%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20and%20Maharashtra.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20time%2C%20the%20yatra%20will%20not%20be%20completely%20conducted%20on%20foot%20like%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20was.%20Instead%2C%20it%20will%20involve%20bus%20travel%20with%20intermittent%20walking%20stretches.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20said%20more%20details%20would%20be%20shared%20later%20with%20the%20media.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECongress%E2%80%99s%20general%20secretary%2C%20communication%2C%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20said%20the%20Bharat%20Nyay%20Yatra%20will%20focus%20on%20social%2C%20economic%2C%20and%20political%20justice%20of%20the%20country%2C%20just%20like%20how%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20had%20focussed%20on%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eissues%20of%20economic%20disparities%2C%C2%A0%20polarisation%2C%20and%20dictatorship%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20party%E2%80%99s%20president%2C%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20will%20flag%20off%20the%20yatra%20from%20Imphal.%20Asked%20why%20Manipur%20was%20chosen%20as%20the%20state%20from%20where%20the%20East-West%20version%20of%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20would%20begin%2C%20the%20Congress%20leaders%20said%20it%20was%20done%20to%20heal%20the%20wounds%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Manipur.%20T