to%20accelerate%20a%20process%20in%20the%20direction%20of%20an%20open%20autocracy%20that%20could%20betoken%2C%20for%20all%20practical%20purposes%2C%20a%20one-party%20state%20apparatus%20%E2%80%93%20bidding%20adieu%20to%20the%20constitution%20we%20have%20nurtured%20for%2075%20years%20%E2%80%93%20if%20circumstances%20remain%20supportive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPredictably%20enough%2C%20in%20the%20short%20run%2C%20the%20most%20critical%20of%20these%20would%20be%20the%20return%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20to%20office%20in%20the%20next%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20five%20months%20away.%20Whether%20as%20a%20propaganda%20trick%20or%20not%2C%20Modi%20has%20recently%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Findia-to-become-third-largest-economy-in-my-third-term-guarantees-pm-modi%2Farticleshow%2F106064170.cms%5C%22%3Edeclared%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20a%20third%20straight%20win%20for%20him%20was%20a%20foregone%20conclusion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20at%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20political%20map%2C%20it%20is%20a%20no-brainer%20that%20an%20effective%20coming%20together%20of%20the%20significant%20sections%20of%20the%20opposition%20in%20the%20major%20states%20will%20block%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20further%20advance%2C%20and%20that%20may%20result%20in%20his%20relegation%20to%20the%20background.%20He%20appears%20to%20have%20way%20too%20many%20adversaries%20within%20the%20saffron%20universe%20who%20could%20turn%20vengeful%20if%20power%20slips%20from%20his%20grasp.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20shots%20in%20Lucknow%2C%20and%20not%20a%20few%20in%20Nagpur%2C%20the%20city%20of%20the%20RSS%20headquarters%2C%20or%20in%20Delhi%2C%20Bhopal%20and%20Jaipur%2C%20to%20say%20nothing%20of%20the%20second%20or%20third%20string%20players%20in%20elsewhere%2C%20who%20now%20pretend%20to%20be%20obsequious%20or%20dutiful%2C%20are%20likely%20to%20lose%20little%20time%20in%20getting%20even%20for%20real%20or%20perceived%20slights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20A%20failure%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20parties%20to%20recognise%20the%20magnitude%20of%20the%20historical%20moment%20they%20are%20navigating%20is%20poised%20to%20leave%20each%20of%20them%20isolated.%20Unity%20is%2C%20therefore%2C%20an%20existential%20imperative.%20Are%20they%20aware%20of%20this%20reality%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20anything%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-morning-after-15-takeaways-from-the-four-state-election-results%23%3A~%3Atext%3DIn%2520the%2520three%2520north%2520Indian%2CBharatiya%2520Janata%2520Party%2520since%25202019.%5C%22%3Erecent%20assembly%20polls%20in%20the%20northern%20states%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20the%20BJP%20won%20decisively%2C%20showed%20that%20the%20local%20Congress%20satraps%20were%20blissfully%20unaware%20of%20the%20great%20political%20significance%20of%20these%20particular%20elections%20and%20carried%20on%20as%20though%20it%20was%20business%20as%20usual.%20So%20was%20the%20Congress%20leadership%2C%20else%20it%20would%20have%20rapped%20the%20three%20erring%20chieftains%20on%20their%20knuckles%20for%20their%20tunnel%20vision%20when%20there%20was%20still%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi%20was%20candid%20enough%20to%20bring%20up%20the%20subject%20in%20the%20December%2021%20meeting%20of%20the%20Congress%20Working%20Committee%20but%2C%20with%20the%20Congress%2C%20there%20is%20no%20knowing%20that%20the%20party%20won%E2%80%99t%20fluff%20its%20lines%20again%20when%20it%20deals%20with%20partners%20and%20allies%20to%20prepare%20for%20the%20parliament%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20being%20displaced%20from%20its%20high%20perch%2030-odd%20years%20ago%20%E2%80%93%20when%20the%20party%20was%20indeed%20a%20gargantuan%20enterprise%20%E2%80%93%20it%20has%20not%20quite%20figured%20out%20how%20to%20operate%20the%20philosophy%20of%20working%20in%20tandem%20with%20entities%20some%20of%20whom%20may%20well%20have%20a%20chip%20on%20their%20shoulder%2C%20being%20state%20parties%20that%20have%20made%20space%20for%20themselves%20by%20edging%20out%20the%20Congress%20over%20time.%20Working%20in%20genuine%20partnership%20with%20the%20Congress%20is%20a%20lesson%20that%20the%20state%20parties%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20also%20need%20to%20learn%20%E2%80%93%20and%20in%20quick%20time.%20There%20is%20not%20much%20time%20left.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComparisons%20of%20the%20present%20situation%20with%20the%20Janata%20experiment%20do%20not%20hold%20water.%20The%20entity%20that%20regional%20parties%20of%20the%20day%20(including%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20precursor%2C%20Jana%20Sangh%2C%20was%20also%20just%20that%20at%20the%20time)%20were%20called%20upon%20to%20ally%20with%20was%20not%20the%20Congress%20but%20a%20disgruntled%20Congress%20rump.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20played%20a%20high-stakes%20game%20in%20the%20recent%20elections%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Chhattisgarh.%20He%20would%20have%20been%20acutely%20conscious%20that%20in%20the%20event%20of%20a%20serious%20setback%20in%20this%20battle%2C%20the%20wolves%20within%20the%20BJP%20would%20be%20out%2C%20baying%20for%20his%20blood.%20They%20would%20question%20his%20ability%20%E2%80%93%20or%20even%20credentials%20%E2%80%93%20to%20lead%20the%20party%20in%20the%20forthcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%20These%20polls%20were%20close%20to%20being%20a%20point%20of%20reckoning%2C%20if%20not%20a%20make%20or%20break%20moment%2C%20for%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20although%20this%20was%20not%20apparent.%20Inherent%20in%20them%20was%20the%20potential%20to%20bring%20the%2010-year%20Modi%20rule%20to%20a%20turning%20point%2C%20whether%20history%20marked%20a%20turn%20or%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20clear%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20Congress%20opponents%20figured%20any%20of%20this.%20They%20did%20not%20discern%20the%20sensitivity%20of%20the%20moment.%20They%20went%20about%20as%20though%20this%20was%20just%20another%20poll%20battle.%20They%20didn%E2%80%99t%20understand%20that%20a%20positive%20result%20would%20give%20Modi%20the%20leap%20and%20momentum%20in%20advance%20of%20the%20key%20election%20in%202024%20and%20help%20him%20set%20the%20field%20for%20the%20main%20battle%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20Modi%20was%20taking%20his%20chances%2C%20he%20was%20not%20playing%20blind%20when%20he%20forced%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20key%20state%20leaders%20%E2%80%93%20the%20architects%20of%20its%20past%20wins%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Chhattisgarh%20%E2%80%93%20out%20of%20the%20reckoning%2C%20appealing%20to%20the%20electorate%20to%20cast%20their%20vote%20in%20his%20name.%20He%20was%20aware%20that%20the%20wind%20of%20communalism%20was%20in%20his%20sails.%20Two%20important%20considerations%20would%20have%20weighed%20as%20inordinately%20powerful%20factors%20%E2%80%93%20Ayodhya%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-leadership-shuffle-generational-change-strategy-for-modi-return%5C%22%3EBJP%E2%80%99s%20Leadership%20Shuffle%3A%20Generational%20Change%20or%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20Strategy%20for%20a%20Return%20to%20Power%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20long%20four-year%20wait%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20decided%20to%20take%20up%20the%20Kashmir%20case%20%E2%80%93%20the%20challenge%20to%20the%20Union%20government%20jettisoning%20the%20constitutional%20autonomy%20of%20J%26amp%3BK.%20The%20arguments%20being%20reported%20in%20the%20press%20gave%20ample%20indication%20which%20way%20things%20were%20going.%20To%20many%20it%20seemed%20that%20the%20timing%20of%20an%20event%20of%20such%20magnitude%20may%20not%20be%20unrelated%20to%20the%20electoral%20timetable.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Ffour-important-takeaways-from-the-supreme-court-ruling-on-jammu-and-kashmir%5C%22%3Ejudgment%3C%2Fa%3E%20came%20on%20December%2011%2C%202023%2C%20after%20the%20recent%20assembly%20election%20results%20were%20announced%2C%20but%20forms%20a%20prelude%20to%20the%20parliament%20election%20due%20early%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArguably%20the%20most%20crucial%20event%20in%20setting%20the%20narrative%20of%20the%20new%20nationalism%20espoused%20by%20Modi%20and%20his%20party%20was%20the%20November%202019%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fayodhya-verdict-supreme-court-judgment%5C%22%3EAyodhya%20judgment%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20called%20the%20destruction%20of%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccriminal%20act%E2%80%9D%20but%20also%2C%20defying%20logic%20and%20common%20sense%2C%20handed%20over%20possession%20of%20the%20site%20on%20which%20it%20had%20stood%20to%20the%20so-called%20Hindu%20parties%2C%20meaning%20a%20clutch%20of%20Hindutva%20outfits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2F07083139%2F2020_8img05_Aug_2020_PTI05-08-2020_000172B.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2F07083139%2F2020_8img05_Aug_2020_PTI05-08-2020_000172B.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2F07083139%2F2020_8img05_Aug_2020_PTI05-08-2020_000172B-300x190.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2F07083139%2F2020_8img05_Aug_2020_PTI05-08-2020_000172B-1024x649.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-471716%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22761%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPM%20Narendra%20Modi%20takes%20part%20in%20the%20bhoomi%20pujan%20for%20the%20construction%20of%20a%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20August%205%2C%202020.%20Photo%3A%20PIB%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20activities%20associated%20with%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20new%20temple%20to%20Lord%20Rama%20have%20been%20flooding%20the%20newspapers%20and%20social%20media.%20They%20have%20also%20found%20a%20regular%20mention%20in%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20speeches%20during%20the%20assembly%20elections.%20The%20inauguration%20of%20the%20temple%20scheduled%20for%20January%2022%2C%202024%2C%20is%20the%20primary%20news%20in%20the%20Modi%20calendar%2C%20and%20is%20dutifully%20reflected%20in%20the%20mainstream%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20background%20became%20the%20setting%20for%20the%20win%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20which%20has%20unbound%20the%20Prometheus%20of%20Hindutva%2C%20who%20is%20portrayed%20as%20a%20heroic%20figure%20%E2%80%93%20greater%20than%20anything%20that%20has%20happened%20to%20the%20Hindu%20supremacist%20ideology%20since%20its%20inception.%20To%20add%20more%20grist%20to%20the%20mill%2C%20the%20temple%20disputes%20of%20Varanasi%20and%20Mathura%20appear%20to%20be%20continually%20stoked%20in%20the%20direction%20desired%20by%20the%20new%20nationalists%20by%20various%20levels%20of%20our%20judicial%20system%2C%20not%20excluding%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20BJP%20leaders%20now%20routinely%20refer%20to%20Modi%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98best%E2%80%99%20prime%20minister%20India%20has%20ever%20had%2C%20clearly%20surpassing%20Vajpayee%20and%20not%20to%20mention%20the%20great%20leaders%20of%20the%20freedom%20movement%2C%20such%20as%20Nehru%2C%20who%20is%20just%20about%20recognized%20as%20a%20former%20prime%20minister%20%E2%80%93%20and%20sought%20to%20be%20made%20less%20than%20significant.%20The%20already-established%20Modi%20cult%20owes%20not%20a%20little%20to%20its%20forceful%20promotion%20by%20Modi%20himself%2C%20who%20seeks%20to%20portray%20himself%20as%20larger%20than%20life%20and%20all-conquering.%20The%20G20%20meet%20in%20Delhi%20this%20year%20was%20an%20illustration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20in%20the%20reign%20of%20this%20cult%20figure%20that%20a%20senior%20functionary%20of%20the%20Ayodhya%20temple%20administration%20has%20declared%20the%20upcoming%20inaugural%20of%20the%20temple%20on%20January%2022%20as%20an%20event%20of%20history%20on%20par%20with%20the%20independence%20of%20India%20from%20British%20rule%20in%201947.%20The%20new%20chief%20minister%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20has%20said%20that%20the%20prime%20meridian%2C%20the%20internationally%20recognised%20zero%20degree%20longitude%20line%2C%20will%20now%20be%20made%20to%20pass%20through%20Ujjain%20in%20his%20state%2C%20which%20is%20the%20seat%20of%20the%20Lord%20Shiva%20as%20Mahakaal%20(the%20Great%20Time).%20The%20currently%20recognised%20marker%20is%20Greenwich%20near%20London%2C%20and%20the%20international%20time%20zones%20are%20calculated%20in%20relation%20to%20Greenwich%20to%20arrive%20at%20Greenwich%20Mean%20Time%20(GMT).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20is%20the%20%E2%80%9Cstrong%20leader%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20Hindutva%20forces%20hanker%20for%2C%20veritably%20the%20current%20%3Cem%3Eavatar%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CChakravarti%20samrat%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20ancient%20India%2C%20a%20mighty%2C%20conquering%20ruler%20who%20cannot%20be%20accountable%20to%20his%20subjects%2C%20and%20who%20is%20beyond%20questioning%20or%20reproach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20it%20is%20no%20surprise%20that%20the%20prime%20minister%20declared%20to%20a%20newspaper%20in%20an%20interview%2C%20ignoring%20the%20parliament%20which%20was%20in%20session%2C%20that%20the%20December%2013%20incident%2C%20which%20saw%20the%20breach%20of%20the%20security%20system%20in%20the%20new%20parliament%20building%20and%20the%20entry%20in%20utterly%20dumbfounding%20circumstances%20of%20some%20youths%2C%20shouting%20slogans%20and%20letting%20off%20smoke-filled%20canisters%2C%20into%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20chamber%2C%20was%20%E2%80%9Cserious%E2%80%9D%2C%20but%20%E2%80%9Cthere%20shall%20be%20no%20debate.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmodi-govts-priorities-an-mps-mimicry-not-146-suspensions%5C%22%3EModi%20Govt%E2%80%99s%20Priority%3A%20An%20MP%E2%80%99s%20Act%20of%20Mimicry%2C%20Caste%20Politics%2C%20Not%20Parliament%20Security%20Breach%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20followed%20was%20predictable%20enough%20as%20the%20presiding%20officers%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20in%20a%20space%20of%20three%20days%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2F141-here-are-all-the-mps-suspended-from-parliament-this-winter-session%5C%22%3Esuspended%3C%2Fa%3E%20nearly%20150%20opposition%20MPs%20because%20they%20made%20a%20ruckus%20and%20showed%20protest%20placards%20when%20their%20demand%20for%20a%20statement%20by%20the%20Union%20home%20minister%20was%20ignored%20by%20the%20Chair.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20all%20practical%20purposes%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20statement%20about%20not%20encountering%20a%20debate%20became%20a%20%3Cem%3Ediktat%20%3C%2Fem%3Efor%20those%20who%20run%20the%20chambers%20of%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20plain%20that%20while%20Prometheus%20may%20have%20now%20broken%20free%2C%20thanks%20to%20multi-sided%20institutional%20capitulation%2C%20the%20institutions%20of%20modern%20India%20are%20themselves%20now%20in%20chains%2C%20waiting%20upon%20the%20will%20of%20the%20master.%20After%20this%2C%20if%20the%20next%20engagement%20is%20in%20the%20bag%20for%20the%20ruler%2C%20we%20may%20only%20anticipate%20a%20turn%20of%20enormous%20magnitude%20in%20our%20constitutional%20and%20political%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20inverted%20reality%20the%20INDIA%20opposition%20alliance%20can%20overlook%20at%20its%20own%20peril%20as%20it%20goes%20about%20in%20its%20inscrutable%20meandering%20fashion%20to%20chart%20out%20an%20electoral%20battle%20plan.%20Grand%20upsets%20are%20a%20part%20of%20history%2C%20including%20our%20own%20not%20so%20distant%20elect